INSERT INTO capture_config (
            workspace_id, path, is_flow, trigger_kind, trigger_config, owner, email
        )
        VALUES (
            $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7
        )
        ON CONFLICT (workspace_id, path, is_flow, trigger_kind)
        DO UPDATE 
        SET 
            trigger_config = $5, 
            owner = $6, 
            email = $7, 
            server_id = NULL, 
            error = NULL
